id: pm-up22
title: Drift-scan cache can false-hit on mtime-preserving file copies
description: history-drift-cache keys on mtime+ctime+size; rsync --archive / cp -p can preserve these and suppress re-verification of a tampered/broken stream -> silent false-ok from pm health.
