  "2026-06-06T10:41:06.967Z",codex-5-3,"Verification preflight: gh api dependabot alerts returned []; secret scanning alerts returned []; code scanning alerts returned HTTP 404 no analysis found and gh reported missing admin:repo_hook scope. Sentry CLI auth is present (scope org:ci) but issue/project APIs return HTTP 403 permission denied. Telemetry health check is healthy with queue_rows_total moving from 2 to 6 after an additional pm list command and last_successful_flush_at populated."
